    "body": "It would be nice if we could support writing bucketing table:\r\n```\r\nval large = spark.range(10e6.toLong)\r\nimport org.apache.spark.sql.SaveMode\r\nlarge.write\r\n  .bucketBy(4, \"id\")\r\n  .sortBy(\"id\")\r\n  .mode(SaveMode.Overwrite)\r\n  .saveAsTable(\"bucketed_4_id\")\r\n```\r\ndriver log:\r\n```\r\n!Exec <DataWritingCommandExec> cannot run on GPU because not all data writing commands can be replaced\r\n  !Output <CreateDataSourceTableAsSelectCommand> cannot run on GPU because bucketing is not supported\r\n  *Exec <RangeExec> will run on GPU\r\n```\r\n",
